---
import { Mail, Linkedin } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section class="pt-[4.8rem] px-6 pb-0">
  <div class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto mb-[3.2rem] text-center fade-in">
    <h2
      class="text-[2.5rem] tracking-tight mb-[1rem] font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent bg-clip-text text-transparent"
    >
      Kind words
    </h2>
    <p
      class="text-[1.1rem] text-base-content/70 leading-[1.8] max-w-[600px] mx-auto"
    >
      Teammates and partners describing what it feels like to build products
      with Kunal day‑to‑day.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div
    class="max-w-[980px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-[2.4rem] fade-in"
  >
    <article
      class="glass glass-card rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] card-gradient transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden group"
    >
      <!-- Decorative accent border -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-transparent rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] group-hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-500"
      >
      </div>

      <!-- Subtle glow effect -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 via-transparent to-accent/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
      >
      </div>

      <div class="card-body p-8 relative z-10">
        <!-- Quote icon -->
        <div
          class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 text-primary/10 text-6xl font-serif opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity duration-500"
        >
          "
        </div>

        <p
          class="text-[1.1rem] text-base-content leading-[1.9] mb-[1.8rem] font-medium relative z-10"
        >
          "Kunal turns ambiguous health problems into crisp design decisions. He
          keeps the room calm, even when stakes and timelines are high."
        </p>

        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-[1.2rem] text-[0.95rem] relative z-10"
        >
          <div
            class="avatar placeholder ring-2 ring-primary/10 group-hover:ring-primary/20 transition-all duration-500"
          >
            <div
              class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-accent text-primary-content rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-500"
            >
              <span class="font-bold text-sm">PM</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <span
              class="block font-semibold text-base-content mb-[0.2rem] group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300"
            >
              Product Manager
            </span>
            <span class="block text-base-content/50 text-sm"> eka.care </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article
      class="glass glass-card rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] transform transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden group"
    >
      <!-- Decorative accent border -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-transparent rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] group-hover:border-accent/20 transition-all duration-500"
      >
      </div>

      <!-- Subtle glow effect -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 via-transparent to-primary/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
      >
      </div>

      <div class="card-body p-8 relative z-10">
        <!-- Quote icon -->
        <div
          class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 text-accent/10 text-6xl font-serif opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity duration-500"
        >
          "
        </div>

        <p
          class="text-[1.1rem] text-base-content leading-[1.9] mb-[1.8rem] font-medium relative z-10"
        >
          "Working with him feels like having a design lead and a facilitator in
          one person. The team ships faster because conversations are clear."
        </p>

        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-[1.2rem] text-[0.95rem] relative z-10"
        >
          <div
            class="avatar placeholder ring-2 ring-accent/10 group-hover:ring-accent/20 transition-all duration-500"
          >
            <div
              class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-primary text-primary-content rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-500"
            >
              <span class="font-bold text-sm">ENG</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <span
              class="block font-semibold text-base-content mb-[0.2rem] group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300"
            >
              Engineering Lead
            </span>
            <span class="block text-base-content/50 text-sm">
              Health platform
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div
    id="contact"
    class="max-w-[820px] mx-auto mt-[3.4rem] glass glass-card rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] overflow-hidden fade-in"
  >
    <div class="card-body p-[2.4rem_2.1rem] text-center relative">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-[-40%] bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_0_0,var(--color-accent),transparent_60%)] opacity-10 pointer-events-none"
      >
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10">
        <h3 class="text-[1.7rem] mb-[0.5rem] tracking-tight font-bold">
          Have a complex product problem?
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-[0.96rem] text-base-content/70 max-w-[32rem] mx-auto mb-[1.6rem] leading-[1.7]"
        >
          Kunal thrives where constraints are real and impact is measurable.
          Share a short brief and he’ll respond with potential next steps or
          questions.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-[0.9rem] flex-wrap">
          <a
            href="mailto:kunal@example.com"
            class="btn btn-primary gap-2 rounded-full shadow-md"
          >
            <Mail size={16} />
            Email Kunal
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/pub/dir/Kunal/Katre"
            class="btn btn-outline gap-2 rounded-full"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
          >
            <Linkedin size={16} />
            Connect on LinkedIn
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
